               <h6>WEBINAR</h6> 
               <h5 style="padding-right: 35.0%;">We helped thousands navigate the Symantec distrust in 2018. Join us for an experience-backed roadmap to avoiding disruption from the Entrust distrust.<br> &nbsp;</h5> 
              </div> 
              <div class="btn-container vertical left" am-region="hp-hero-control-01-survey"> <a href="https://digicert.registration.goldcast.io/events/6e4d709a-e4fe-4d04-bdc7-b9fd44807c9b" class="btn primary blue" target="_blank">WATCH NOW</a> 
