    <section class="frame frame--hero"> 
     <div class="frame__content"> 
      <section class="hero
      
      hero--index hero--flush-desktop-padding-left hero--index-alt hero-2020-08
" ng-controller="domainSearchController as domainSearchCtrl"> 
       <div class="hero__content"> 
        <div class="hero__title  "> <span aria-level="2" role="heading" class="text
"> An update on domains </span> 
        </div> 
        <div class="hero__subtitle"> 
         <p><span class="text
"> Google no longer offers new domain registrations, but try&nbsp;Squarespace </span></p> 
        </div> 
        <div class="hero__buttons"> <a class="button " href="https://domains.squarespace.com/?channel=bd&amp;subchannel=google-domain&amp;campaign=&amp;subcampaign=&amp;source=google_domain_referral&amp;utm_source=google_domain_referral&amp;utm_medium=bd&amp;utm_content=google-domain&amp;utm_term=utm_campaign=" rel="noreferrer noopener" target="_blank" data-ga4-event="dahlia_select" data-ga4-eventparams="{&quot;contentType&quot;: &quot;cta&quot;, &quot;moduleName&quot;: &quot;purchase domain squarespace&quot;, &quot;itemId&quot;: &quot;purchase domain squarespace - hero&quot;}"> <span class="text
"> Get a new domain from&nbsp;Squarespace </span> </a> 
        </div> 
        <div class="hero__body"> 
         <p><span class="text
"> On September 7, 2023 Squarespace acquired all domain registrations and related customer accounts from Google Domains. <br><br> All customer accounts and domains have been migrated to <a href="https://domains.squarespace.com/">Squarespace Domains</a>. <br><br> <a href="https://support.squarespace.com/hc/">For questions or support, contact Squarespace.</a> </span></p> 
        </div> 
        <div class="hero__footnote"> <span class="text
"> This is an affiliate link. If you make a purchase from Squarespace, we may earn a&nbsp;commission. </span> 
        </div> 
